text: Carine may refer to: * Carine (Mysia), a town of ancient Mysia, now in Turkey * Carine, Western Australia, a suburb of Perth * Electoral district of Carine, in the Western Australian parliament, including the suburb * some species of owls, including ** Little owl (Carine noctua or Athene noctua) ** Rodrigues owl (Carine murivora or Mascarenotus murivorus) * Guzmania 'Carine', a bromeliad hybrid cultivar * Carine (given name) * CARINE, theorem prover, a mathematical concept ==See also== * Carina (disambiguation)
title: Carine
